{"tid":1850731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"買口罩排隊有咩想同政府講? 市民: 叫佢地食屎啦","createTime":"2020-01-29T16:30:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T17:18:35.000Z","uid":71393,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2e592e9adcad1c4a5e0198c060c36a188668bf55","tid":1850731,"uid":71393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:30:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x2amnKQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx2amnKQ.jpg&h=c97fe0d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【武漢肺炎】野蠻大媽買唔到口罩圍阿布泰 過百街坊聲援救老細<br />\n<br />\n「阿布泰」創辦人林景楠表示，今次售賣的口罩在短短兩小時內售罄，有街坊抱怨排隊多個小時仍未能成功購買口罩，感到鼓譟，隨即包圍分店。林景楠指該批不滿的街坊均覺得，為何阿布泰優先售賣口罩予醫護人員及紀律部隊，「我避免咗有任何衝突，咁我都留咗喺舖頭入面，過咗一陣，其他市民過到嚟講解咗，呼籲佢哋離開，咁最後我就安全地離開」。林景楠續指，阿布泰所出售的口罩大部份泰國製造，但現時仍未有實際數字，所以未知今日共出售多少個口罩，「縱使嚟緊再返貨，但香港有700萬人口，返幾多口罩都唔能夠足以應付，畀到700萬人去使用，因為使用量太大，而且每日都要更換口罩，咁多個商家暫時都滿足唔到」。對於政府聲稱稍後會增加貨源，他語氣平淡表示：「加油，希望政府可以做得到」，然後又指全面封鎖邊境關口，避免疫症在香港爆發才是最根本的解決方法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200129/RPDQNNJA56FJ7QK24NZVMEEFU4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2ZwMiPJbYqopgaxFFUVcg5Ym40PZ957XMdOph27uHjGoh9a5w1fYrLPBc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200129%2FRPDQNNJA56FJ7QK24NZVMEEFU4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2ZwMiPJbYqopgaxFFUVcg5Ym40PZ957XMdOph27uHjGoh9a5w1fYrLPBc&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBH2vf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=cb6ff0dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200129%2FRPDQNNJA56FJ7QK24NZVMEEFU4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2ZwMiPJbYqopgaxFFUVcg5Ym40PZ957XMdOph27uHjGoh9a5w1fYrLPBc&h=ad393a01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200129/RPDQNNJA56FJ7QK24NZVMEEFU4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2ZwMiPJbYqopgaxFFUVcg5Ym40PZ957XMdOph27uHjGoh9a5w1fYrLPBc</a>"},{"pid":"62c6bed84bfdcc811b3ada7857cc434fff3d5354","tid":1850731,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:31:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/308/5d9705d903228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F308%2F5d9705d903228.jpg&h=786cb045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港共正利用武漢肺炎進行第9步：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">種族清洗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n透過邊境不設防<br />\n高調宣揚非本地人士免費優先治療武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蓄意引導大量染病支那人來港<br />\n摧毀香港已經長期超負荷的醫療系統，令香港人大規模感染<br />\n而無法隔離或治理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>意圖對香港人進行大屠殺</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港獨立 港中區隔"},{"pid":"94b297b8311eb46a204fce11f83e949c5d2700dd","tid":1850731,"uid":231583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:34:49.000Z","msg":"先售賣口罩予醫護人員及紀律部隊，應該有講明唔包黑警？"},{"pid":"5f4c1b4c34e21f42197b49a2f61ee24c38ab7e3b","tid":1850731,"uid":252877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:51:25.000Z","msg":"吊鳩林鄭個仆街政府<img src=\"